{"tid":878371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州小四生遭龍門架砸死 傳校方指閉路電視故障","createTime":"2018-10-27T05:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T07:29:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2270749066443f4d8a22c1279bf239757d72aa24","tid":878371,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540547466_02d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540547466_02d4.jpg&h=9ff1a475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒今日報道，廣州增城區一小學發生奪命意外，一名四年級學生被倒下的龍門架砸死。<br />\n<br />\n涉事學校新塘鎮香江小學昨日(25日)通報，小四學生孫瑜澤於周二(23日)上體育課期間，被運動場的龍門架砸中死亡。惟網上有自稱是死者家屬朋友的網民指，家人事後曾到學校，希望校方可以給予一個滿意的答覆，但校方一拖再拖，負責人更拒絕出面。家人在校門前擺放蠟燭等進行路祭但被趕，又指校方曾指閉路電視拍下事發過程，事後又稱系統故障。<br />\n<br />\n家屬又指，校方原先指學生腿部被卡，用力掙脫時令龍門架倒下。不過體育老師卻透露，是有四、五個學生搬動龍門架時，意外砸死學生。校方在通報中，表示會為事件負責，更指會與家屬協商。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540547466_fd8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540547466_fd8e.jpg&h=b61a0427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540547466_52b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540547466_52b6.jpg&h=df9976c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181026/58839385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F58839385&d=9tSyKLBB3qJDh42hBz%2B1MHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1cc3b4fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F58839385&h=8717fd3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181026/58839385</a>"},{"pid":"60a222b8f301a938bbf226668c529de27c79c4c6","tid":878371,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:45:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e755a254dfe2e929fcefa50688b25b0cc5c90eda","tid":878371,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"搬龍門搬得太多"},{"pid":"76d37036c7085b7bd0e7d3baecf361c4fa444333","tid":878371,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"大陸d 建築不嬲好危險<br />\n冧牆壓死人, 大型重物壓死人呢d 聽唔少"},{"pid":"3f09ccd06a31a04bdeac5b89c4c4e3ff0c262f1d","tid":878371,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b4cc6599042f6d1211f1b4ab5c5e4c6678e2a14","tid":878371,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"點會係有班小學生推龍門, 根本推唔郁<br />\n<br />\n我估應該係班小學雞當龍門係馬嬲架玩<br />\n<br />\n點知反撚左<br />\n<br />\n而閉路電視故障係因為影到有老師係附近無阻止,事後無急救<br />\n<br />\n一放片就要賠錢"},{"pid":"27953331c56e9f63ef3aebb082730baadaa938d7","tid":878371,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e755a254dfe2e929fcefa50688b25b0cc5c90eda","tid":878371,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"搬龍門搬得太多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:22:21.000Z","msg":"上得山多終遇虎"},{"pid":"f55fa205b8cdc4031e50c1e8fe640fc200008a32","tid":878371,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"閉路永遠出事嗰陣就會壞"}]}